products.description: Free 2-Day Shipping: When you use your Target CircleTM Card (debit, credit, and reloadable) for your Target.com purchases or are a Target Circle 360TM member, you receive free standard shipping on most items and free 2-day shipping on eligible items. Hundreds of thousands of items qualify for 2-day shipping. Item eligibility and assortment vary by market and are determined by the location of the item and the destination ZIP code.
